text: Takahashi Inari Shrine (高橋稲荷神社, Takahashi inari jinja) is a Shinto shrine that worships the kami Inari. It is in Kumamoto. Its main festival is held annually on November 8. It was built in 1496. It is an unranked shrine in the Modern system of ranked Shinto shrines. == Other websites == Category:Beppyo shrines Category:Unranked shrines Category:Pages with unreviewed translations Category:Shinto shrines in Kumamoto Prefecture
